dc_description_s: Relief shown by 5 feet contour interval and spot heights. Map shows district, municipal or town, property and cadastral boundaries. Includes index to sheets. "Surveyed, constructed and drawn by the Department of Lands and Surveys, Uganda, 1959-1960. Revised by the Department of Lands and Surveys, September 1967." "The representation on this map of a road, track or footpath is no evidence of a right of way." "Cadastral boundaries as shown on this map do not in any way affect the boundaries shown in Registered Titles." "300-1-68." ©Copyright Uganda Government 1968
